          "name": "Powerful Defiance",
          "description": "This unit cannot be stunned or be sent to the reinforcements from the battlefield.\n\nThis unit's attacks grant hit targets the Burn status effect after damage is dealt.\n\nBurn will overwrite other status effects on affected units. Any unit that deals damage to or is dealt damage by a unit with Burn will gain the Burn status effect."
