        "id": "BattlewornPassiveAManchesterRegularBoss",
        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Exorcist Training",
          "description": "This unit enters battle Fortified, and with a Sleep Ward, and a Poison Ward.\n\nIf this unit would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP.\n\nEach time this unit takes damage from an attack and survives until after the end of the turn, this unit will be granted a Charge. Certain skills are affected by and may consume charges. A unit can store a maximum of 3 charges, and all charges are removed from a unit that leaves the battlefield."
